Question-4 
Write a java program to convert kilometres to mile.

import java.util.Scanner;
public class KmToMiles {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        // 1. Ask the user for the distance in kilometers
        System.out.print("Enter distance in Kilometers: ");
        double km = sc.nextDouble();
        // 2. Perform the conversion math
        // Factor: 1 km = 0.621371 miles
        double miles = km * 0.621371;
        // 3. Display the result
        System.out.println(km + " Kilometers is equal to " + miles + " Miles.");
        sc.close();
    }
}
Output:
Enter distance in Kilometers: 18
18.0 Kilometers is equal to 11.184678 Miles.

